time to set up some very specific rules for what will result in banning someone from a CoG event.  And no, someone rolling a 199 against you does NOT count as a reason for banning  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><HR>
